<script type="text/javascript">
toastr.options = {
"closeButton": true,
"timeOut": 6000,
"extendedTimeOut": 2000,
};

$(document).ready(function() {
$(document).on('click', '.btn-customize', function(e) {
e.preventDefault();

$('#modal-customize').data('project-id', $(this).data('project-id'));
$('.dropdown-random-bid-skills').html('');
$('#input-customize').val('')
var skills = $(this).data('skills').split('~');
$.each(skills, function(index, val) {
var skill = val.split('=');
$('.dropdown-random-bid-skills').append('<button type="button" class="dropdown-item btn-generate-random-bid" data-skill-id="'+skill[0]+'">'+skill[1]+'</button>');
});

$('#modal-customize .modal-budget-string').html($(this).data('budget-string'));
$('#modal-customize .modal-currency-code').html($(this).data('currency-code'));
$('#modal-customize .bid_price').val($(this).data('bid-price'));
});

$(document).on('click', '.btn-generate-random-bid', function(e) {
e.preventDefault();

var btn = $(this);
$.ajax({
type: "post",
url: "get_random_bid.php",
data: 'project_id='+$('#modal-customize').data('project-id')+'&skill_id='+btn.data('skill-id'),
beforeSend: function() {
btn.parents('.btn-group').children('.btn-generate-random-bid').html('<i class="fa fa-spinner fa-spin"></i>');
btn.parents('.btn-group').find('.btn-generate-random-bid').prop('disabled', 'disabled');
}
})
.done(function(Response) {
if (Response != 'ERROR')
{
$('#input-customize').val(Response);
}
else
{
toastr["error"]('Error generating random bid');
}
})
.fail(function() {

})
.always(function() {
btn.parents('.btn-group').children('.btn-generate-random-bid').html('Generate Random Bid');
btn.parents('.btn-group').find('.btn-generate-random-bid').prop('disabled', '');
});
});

$(document).on('submit', '#form-customize-bid', function(e) {
e.preventDefault();

var btn = $('.btn-place-customize-bid');
$.ajax({
type: "post",
url: "place_bid.php",
data: 'project_id='+$('#modal-customize').data('project-id')+'&bid='+escape($('#input-customize').val())+'&bid_price='+$('#modal-customize .bid_price').val(),
beforeSend: function() {
btn.html('<i class="fa fa-spinner fa-spin"></i>');
btn.prop('disabled', 'disabled');

$('.btn-customize[data-project-id='+$('#modal-customize').data('project-id')+']').parents('.search-result-item').find('.bid-buttons .info-card-details').remove();
}
})
.done(function(Response) {
//Response = jQuery.parseJSON(Response);
if (Response['ErrorCode'] == '000')
{
$('#modal-customize').modal('hide');
$('#input-customize').val('');
toastr["success"]("Bid placed successfully");
$('.btn-customize[data-project-id='+$('#modal-customize').data('project-id')+']').parents('.search-result-item').find('.bid_price').parent().html(Response['Amount']);
$('.btn-customize[data-project-id='+$('#modal-customize').data('project-id')+']').parents('.search-result-item').find('.btn-automatic-bid-skill').removeClass('btn-automatic-bid-skill').removeAttr('href').removeAttr('data-project-id').removeAttr('data-skill-id');
$('.btn-customize[data-project-id='+$('#modal-customize').data('project-id')+']').parents('.bid-buttons').html(`<div class="info-card-details">
<span class="icon">
<svg class="icon-image" width="18" height="18" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 30 30"><path fill="#2653d4" d="M12.042 2c-5.523 0-10 4.477-10 10s4.477 10 10 10 10-4.477 10-10-4.478-10-10-10zm-.75 15.75l-5-3.75 1.5-2 3 2.25 5.25-7 2 1.5-6.75 9z"></path></svg>
</span>
<span class="text-primary">
You have already bid on this project.
</span>
</div>`);
$('#modal-customize').data('project-id', '');
}
else if (Response['ErrorCode'] == '100')
{
toastr["error"](Response['Message']);
$('.btn-customize[data-project-id='+$('#modal-customize').data('project-id')+']').parents('.bid-buttons').prepend(`<div class="info-card-details">
<span class="icon">
<svg class="icon-image" width="18" height="18" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 30 30"><path fill="#e74a3b" d="M9,0C4.1,0,0,4,0,9s4.1,9,9,9s9-4.1,9-9S14,0,9,0z M13.5,11.9c0.4,0.4,0.4,1.1,0,1.5c-0.4,0.4-1.1,0.4-1.5,0L9,10.5l-3,2.9c-0.4,0.4-1.1,0.4-1.5,0c-0.4-0.4-0.4-1.1,0-1.5L7.5,9L4.5,6c-0.4-0.4-0.4-1.1,0-1.5c0.4-0.4,1.1-0.4,1.5,0l3,2.9L12,4.5c0.4-0.4,1.1-0.4,1.5,0c0.4,0.4,0.4,1.1,0,1.5L10.5,9L13.5,11.9z"/></svg>
</span>
<span class="text-danger">
`+Response['Message']+`

}
else if (Response['ErrorCode'] == '101')
{

var lastCount = '0';

setInterval(function() {
$.ajax({
type: "post",
url: "check_new_projects.php",
})
.done(function(Response) {
Response = jQuery.parseJSON(Response);
// if (lastCount != Response['Total'])
// {
// new Audio('notification.mp3').play();
// }

lastCount = Response['Total'];

if (Response['Total'] == '0')
{
$('.search-result-newProjectAlert').hide();
}
else
{
$('.search-result-newProjectAlert').show();
$('.search-result-newProjectAlert-icon').html('View '+Response['Total']+' new jobs');
}

if (Response['Projects'].length > 0)
{
new Audio('notification.mp3').play();
}

$('.text-ai_bids_left').html(Response['ai_bids_left'])

$.each(Response['Projects'], function(index, value) {
var html = '';
html += '<h6 class="toast-project-title">'+value['title']+'</h6>';
html += '<p class="toast-project-skills">'+value['job_string']+'</p>';
html += '<p class="toastAddedText toast-project-description">'+value['description']+'</p>';

if (value['min_budget'] && value['max_budget'])
{
html += '<div class="notification-project-price">'+value['currency_sign']+value['min_budget']+' - '+value['currency_sign']+value['max_budget']+' '+value['currency_code']+(value['type'] == 'hourly' ? ' per hour' : '')+'</div>';
}
else if (value['min_budget'] && !value['max_budget'])
{
html += '<div class="notification-project-price">'+value['currency_sign']+value['min_budget']+' '+value['currency_code']+(value['type'] == 'hourly' ? ' per hour' : '')+'</div>';
}
else
{
html += '<div class="notification-project-price">Upto '+value['currency_sign']+value['max_budget']+' '+value['currency_code']+(value['type'] == 'hourly' ? ' per hour' : '')+'</div>';
}

html += `
<div class="row">
<div class="col-6"><button class="btn btn-success btn-block btn-sm btn-automatic-bid" data-notification="true" data-project-id="`+value['id']+`">Place Bid</button></div>
<div class="col-6"><button class="btn btn-primary btn-block btn-sm btn-customize" data-project-id="`+value['id']+`" data-bid-price="`+value['bid_price']+`" data-budget-string="`+value['budget_string']+`" data-currency-code="`+value['currency_code']+`" data-skills="`+value['project_jobs']+`" type="button" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#modal-customize">Customize</button></div>
</div>
`;

toastr["info"](html);
});
})
.fail(function() {
});
}, 4000);
